The paper deals with topics related to information theory, cryptography, and computational complexity, which are covered by the cs.IT, cs.CR, and cs.CC sub-categories. The use of lattices and their properties in the analysis also suggests the cs.DS sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the implications of a conjecture, which could be considered a topic in social implications of technology, covered by the cs.SI sub-category.
